*       text
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
*      -->P_SIZE  text
*      -->P_BOLD  text
*      -->P_UNDERLINE  text
*      -->P_WRAPTEXT  text
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM set_font  USING    p_size
                        p_bold
                        p_underline .
  CALL METHOD OF go_range 'FONT' = go_font .

  SET PROPERTY OF go_font 'Size' = p_size .
  SET PROPERTY OF go_font 'Bold' = p_bold .
  SET PROPERTY OF go_font 'Underline' = p_underline .
ENDFORM.

